                             <li>Next years Tri Nations   test between the Springboks and All Blacks will be played on 20th Aug   2011 in the new Nelson Mandela Bay   stadium in Port   Elizabeth. We&rsquo;ll be hosting train tours from Jo&rsquo;burg and   Cape Town to PE   respectively </li>
